text: GBW is the reporting mark for Green Bay and Western Railroad It may also refer to: * gbw, an ISO 639-3 designator for the Gabi-Gabi language * Gain–bandwidth product * Georgian Business Week, an English-language newspaper in Tbilisi, Georgia * Ghribwal railway station, in Pakistan * Glenbard West High School, in Chicago, Illinois * Guild of Bookworkers, an American bookbinding organization
title: GBW (disambiguation)
